     Annual Board Fee
   Title 13 CCR § 553

    A. Notice of proposed action
       A1. Notice of Change of Public Hearing
    B. Initial statement of reasons
    C. Text of regulation
    D. Final statement of reasons
    E. OAL's decision on the regulation
       E1. On October 30, 2001, the Office of Administrative Law
       approved the Board's proposed regulatory action.
    F. The date the regulation was filed with the Secretary of State
       F1. On October 30, 2001, the regulation was filed with the
       Secretary
       of State.
    G. The effective date of the regulation
       G1. The regulation will take effect on December 31, 2001.
    H. Notice of intent of the agency to discontinue the proposed action
       (if applicable)

